metadata.name: HĒRA
metadata.description:
The queen of titans and the goddess of skies.

Its foreseeing vision and ancient wisdom of worlds has transcended the physical boundaries as an inspiring message to all leaders to keep on building and restore the fallen lands of Xen.

It is said that Hēra would appear to those who carry a profound message, in their dreams, floating in an endless path where the skies collapse.


Made by: XENOTRIP
JPEG: 4000x5000 px
